Corinne Touzet https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Corinne_Touzet 0 Corinne Touzet (born 21 December 1959) is a French actress and producer. She is best known for her starring role as Isabelle Florent in the French police drama series Une femme d'honneur which ran from 1996 - 2008.
